  • example使用的example中的类 
    类和说明
    Flag
    A generic synchronized flag, because Java doesn't have one.
    FullScreenWindow
    A window that takes over the full screen.
    PageChangeListener
    A listener to indicate that some control has asked for a particular page to be displayed.
    PagePanel
    A Swing-based panel that displays a PDF page image.
    PDFPrintPage
    A class representing a print job for a particular PDFFile.
    PDFViewer.PageBuilder
    Combines numeric key presses to build a multi-digit page number.
    PDFViewer.PagePreparer
    A class to pre-cache the next page for better UI response
    PDFViewer.ThumbAction 
    PDFViewer.ZoomAction 
    ThumbPanel
    A panel of thumbnails, one for each page of a PDFFile.
